lines.text: Hello. There's a lot of people out there! How ya doin'? One moment, please.

Now do me a favor and sit down - okay? Tonight we're gonna do a very long show - I don't want your legs to get tired, so move back, and sit down and be comfortable. Do it, do it. I don't want to have any problems with people getting mashed here in the front, so please relax.
